---
import LegalPageLayout from "../layouts/LegalPageLayout.astro";
---

<LegalPageLayout
  title="Support — CheqSplit"
  description="Contact CheqSplit for help, bugs, or feedback. Common questions and legal links."
  canonicalPath="/support/"
>
  <article class="legal-doc text-slate-800" aria-labelledby="support-title">
    <header class="mb-10 border-b border-slate-200 pb-8">
      <h1 id="support-title" class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 md:text-4xl">Support — CheqSplit</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-10 text-base leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Thank you for using CheqSplit. If you need help, run into a problem, or have feedback, we’re here for you.
      </p>

      <section class="space-y-4" aria-labelledby="contact-email">
        <h2 id="contact-email" class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Contact us by email</h2>
        <p>
          <a class="font-medium text-brand-600 underline hover:text-brand-700" href="mailto:lungusterus@gmail.com"
            >lungusterus@gmail.com</a
          >
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
          Note: We try to reply within a few business days. Please include your device model (e.g. iPhone 15) and iOS version if you’re reporting a bug.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4" aria-labelledby="faq-support">
        <h2 id="faq-support" class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Common questions</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-4 pl-6">
          <li>
            <strong>Receipt scan looks wrong.</strong> Try cropping the receipt clearly, retake the photo with good light, and review or edit line items on the next screen before starting a split.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Can’t join or share a bill.</strong> Check your internet connection and that you’re using the latest app version from the App Store.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Subscriptions or billing.</strong> Purchases are handled by Apple. You can manage or cancel them in{" "}
            <strong>Settings → [Your Name] → Subscriptions</strong> on your iPhone.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4" aria-labelledby="legal-support">
        <h2 id="legal-support" class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Legal</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
          <li><a class="font-medium text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700" href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a></li>
          <li><a class="font-medium text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700" href="/terms-of-service/">Terms of Service</a></li>
          <li>
            <a class="font-medium text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700" href="/delete-account/">Delete your account (Google Play)</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a class="font-medium text-brand-600 hover:text-brand-700" href="/delete-data/">Delete your data (Google Play)</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
        <strong>Developer:</strong> Lunthemes
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</LegalPageLayout>
